OL,3,CFirst Minister leads tributes to Pope
OL,4,CFrancis who's died at the age of 88
OL,6,FWales' First Minister Eluned Morgan MS
OL,7,Fhas paid tribute to Pope Francis who
OL,8,Fhas died at the age of 88.
OL,10,FThe Vatican said in a statement on
OL,11,FMonday morning: "At 7:35 this morning
OL,12,F(local time), the Bishop of Rome,
OL,13,FFrancis, returned to the house of the
OL,14,FFather. His entire life was dedicated
OL,15,Fto the service of the Lord and His
OL,16,FChurch."
OL,18,FThe pope was last seen in public on
OL,19,FEaster Sunday, where he blessed
OL,20,Fthousands of people in St. Peter's
OL,21,FSquare.
