OL,3,CFirst Minister leads tributes to Pope
OL,4,CFrancis who's died at the age of 88
OL,6,FIn a statement, Ms Morgan said: "It is
OL,7,Fwith great sadness that I have learned
OL,8,Fof the passing of His Holiness Pope
OL,9,FFrancis.
OL,11,F"As First Minister of Wales, and as a
OL,12,FChristian, I offer my deepest
OL,13,Fcondolences to the Catholic community
OL,14,Fin Wales and around the world.
