OL,3,CFirst Minister leads tributes to Pope
OL,4,CFrancis who's died at the age of 88
OL,6,F"His famous call to 'not judge, but
OL,7,Fwalk with' exemplified a faith rooted
OL,8,Fin love, empathy and understanding for
OL,9,Fall people, focusing on compassion
OL,10,Frather than condemnation.
OL,12,F"In his final months, he spoke with
OL,13,Fmoral clarity, condemning what he
OL,14,Freferred to as the 'genocide' in Gaza,
OL,15,Furging the world to recognise the
OL,16,Fhumanity of all people and to choose
OL,17,Fpeace over destruction.
