OL,3,CFirst Minister leads tributes to Pope
OL,4,CFrancis who's died at the age of 88
OL,6,F"In a world that often feels divided,
OL,7,FPope Francis built bridges of unity
OL,8,Fand his legacy will endure in the
OL,9,Flives he touched and the values he
OL,10,Fchampioned - values that continue to
OL,11,Finspire us here in Wales.
OL,13,F"On behalf of the Welsh Government, I
OL,14,Foffer our deepest sympathies to all
OL,15,Fthose mourning his loss. May he rest
OL,16,Fin peace, and may his example continue
OL,17,Fto guide and inspire us all."
